w features to be notified of a session reconnect, in case resubmit content\n    39→   *\n    40→   * @param callback invoked when the session reconnects\n    41→   * @returns a callback id to be used to unsubscribe from the callback store\n    42→   */\n    43→  subscribeToSessionReconnect(callback: () => void): string;\n    44→\n    45→  /**\n    46→   * Unsubscribes the callback matching callbackId from session reconnect listeners\n    47→   * @param callbackId callback id to be used to unsubscribe from the callback store\n    48→   */\n    49→  unsubscribeFromSessionReconnect(callbackId: string): void;\n    50→\n    51→  /**\n    52→   * Returns false if the session has been closed or we don't have a session.\n    53→   * Session is guaranteed to be open while the container is open, no need to check in container code\n    54→   * Used by host code that caches container AugmentationSession to access page AL content\n    55→\n    56→   * @returns true if there's an open session, false otherwise\n    57→   */\n    58→  isSessionActive(): boolean;\n    59→}\n    60→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01LamMSZH4D3xtZzNhF4Uoq8","session_id":"8a2fc4e6-c1a3-49e6-ae99-e4ee481c1eee","uuid":"00926534-a478-4614-acfa-81bb209d38b8"}
