ible = useUiStore((s) => s.setMetaChatModalVisible)\n    37→\n    38→\tconst onSectionToggled = (index: number) => () => {\n    39→\t\tsetExpandedSections((prev) =>\n    40→\t\t\tprev.includes(index) ? prev.filter((i) => i !== index) : [...prev, index]\n    41→\t\t)\n    42→\t}\n    43→\n    44→\tconst getThoughtTimeout = () => {\n    45→\t\tconst lastStep = cotProcessingSteps?.[cotProcessingSteps.length - 1]\n    46→\t\tif (!lastStep) return 1000\n    47→\t\tconst numThoughts = lastStep.thoughts?.length ?? 1\n    48→\t\tlet stepTime = lastStep.delay ?? 5000\n    49→\n    50→\t\tif (latencyTiming === LatencyTiming.P75) {\n    51→\t\t\tstepTime *= 0.576\n    52→\t\t}\n    53→\t\tif (latencyTiming === LatencyTiming.P50) {\n    54→\t\t\tstepTime *= 0.467\n    55→\t\t}\n    56→\n    57→\t\treturn stepTime / (numThoughts + 1)\n    58→\t}\n    59→\n    60→\tconst getActionTimeout = () => {\n    61→\t\tconst lastStep = cotProcessingSteps?.[cotProcessingSteps.length - 1]\n    62→\t\tif (!lastStep) return 500\n    63→\n    64→\t\tconst numActions = lastStep.thoughts?.[currentThought]?.actions?.length ?? 1\n    65→\t\tconst thoughtTime = getThoughtTimeout()\n    66→\n    67→\t\treturn thoughtTime / (numActions + 1)\n    68→\t}\n    69→\n    70→\tconst onActionButtonClicked = (label: string) => {\n    71→\t\tif (label === 'Manage memory topic') {\n    72→\t\t\tsetMetaChatModalVisible(true)\n    73→\t\t}\n    74→\t}\n    75→\n    76→\tuseInterval(\n    77→\t\t() => {\n    78→\t\t\tsetCurrentAction(0)\n    79→\t\t\tsetCurrentThought((prev) => prev + 1)\n    80→\t\t},\n    81→\t\tisComplete ? null : getThoughtTimeout()\n    82→\t)\n    83→\n    84→\tuseInterval(\n    85→\t\t() => {\n    86→\t\t\tsetCurrentAction((prev) => prev + 1)\n    87→\t\t},\n    88→\t\tisComplete ? null : getActionTimeout()\n    89→\t)\n    90→\n    91→\tuseEffect(() => {\n    92→\t\t// set processingSteps as an internal state so it updates at the same time as the thought and action counts\n    93→\t\t// otherwise it throws off the list size and causes a card size glitch\n    94→\n    95→\t\tsetCurrentAction(0)\n    96→\t\tsetCurrentThought(0)\n    97→\t\tsetProcessingSteps(props.cotProcessingSteps ?? [])\n    98→\n    99→\t\tif (!autoCollapseChainOfThought) {\n   100→\t\t\tconst index = props.cotProcessingSteps?.length\n   101→\t\t\tif (index === undefined) return\n   102→\t\t\tsetExpandedSections((prev) => [...prev, index])\n   103→\t\t}\n   104→\t}, [props.cotProcessingSteps])\n   105→\n   106→\tuseEffect(() => {\n   107→\t\t// wait 500 ms\n   108→\t\t// then set the initial render to false\n   109→\t\tconst timer = setTimeout(() => {\n   110→\t\t\tsetIsInitialRender(false)\n   111→\t\t}, 500)\n   112→\t\treturn () => clearTimeout(timer)\n   113→\t}, [])\n   114→\n   115→\t// @ts-ignore\n   116→\tconst renderDetailedStatusItem = (step: CoTProcessingStep, stepIndex: number) => {\n   117→\t\tconst isLastStep = cotProcessingSteps && stepIndex === cotProcessingSteps.length - 1\n   118→\t\tconst isExpanded = expandedSections.includes(stepIndex) || (isLastStep && !isComplete)\n   119→\n   120→\t\treturn (\n   121→\t\t\t<DetailedStatusItem>\n   122→\t\t\t\t<TitleBar onClick={onSectionToggled(stepIndex)}>\n   123→\t\t\t\t\t<Body1Strong style={{ flex: 1 }}>{step.title}</Body1Strong>\n   124→\t\t\t\t\t{isExpanded ? <ChevronDown12Regular /> : <ChevronUp12Regular />}\n   125→\t\t\t\t</TitleBar>\n   126→\t\t\t\t<CollapsibleContent\n   127→\t\t\t\t\tinitial={isInitialRender ? { height: 'auto', opacity: 1 } : { height: 0, opacity: 0 }}\n   128→\t\t\t\t\tanimate={isExpanded ? { height: 'auto', opacity: 1 } : { height: 0, opacity: 0 }}\n   129→\t\t\t\t\ttransition={{ duration: 0.2 }}\n   130→\t\t\t\t>\n   131→\t\t\t\t\t{step.thoughts?.map((thought, i) => {\n   132→\t\t\t\t\t\tconst isLastThought = i === currentThought\n   133→\t\t\t\t\t\tif (streamIndividualThoughts && isLastStep && i > currentThought) return null\n   134→\t\t\t\t\t\tif (isInitialRender) return null\n   135→\t\t\t\t\t\treturn (\n   136→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ThoughtContainer\n   137→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tkey={i}\n   138→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tinitial={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}\n   139→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tanimate={{ opacity: 1, height: 'auto' }}\n   140→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t>\n   141→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<Caption1>{thought.text}</Caption1>\n   142→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{thought.actions && thought.actions.length > 0 && (\n   143→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ActionsContainer>\n   144→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{thought.actions?.map((action, j: number) => {\n   145→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tif (\n   146→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tstreamIndividualThoughts &&\n   147→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tisLastStep &&\n   148→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tisLastThought &&\n   149→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tj >= currentAction\n   150→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t)\n   151→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\treturn null\n   152→\n   153→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\treturn (\n   154→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<BadgeContainer\n   155→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tkey={j}\n   156→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tinitial={{ opacity: 0, height: 0 }}\n   157→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tanimate={{ opacity: 1, height: 'auto' }}\n   158→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t>\n   159→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<StyledBadge icon={action.icon} color=\"informative\" size=\"large\">\n   160→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{action.text}\n   161→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</StyledBadge>\n   162→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</BadgeContainer>\n   163→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t)\n   164→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t})}\n   165→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ActionsContainer>\n   166→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t)}\n   167→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ThoughtContainer>\n   168→\t\t\t\t\t\t)\n   169→\t\t\t\t\t})}\n   170→\t\t\t\t</CollapsibleContent>\n   171→\t\t\t</DetailedStatusItem>\n   172→\t\t)\n   173→\t}\n   174→\n   175→\treturn (\n   176→\t\t<Container>\n   177→\t\t\t{cotProcessingSteps?.map((step, i) => (\n   178→\t\t\t\t<StatusItem\n   179→\t\t\t\t\tkey={i}\n   180→\t\t\t\t\tinitial={isInitialRender ? { opacity: 1, height: 'auto' } : { opacity: 0, height: 0 }}\n   181→\t\t\t\t\tanimate={{ opacity: 1, height: 'auto' }}\n   182→\t\t\t\t\ttransition={{ duration: 0.35 }}\n   183→\t\t\t\t>\n   184→\t\t\t\t\t<StatusSpinner\n   185→\t\t\t\t\t\tstate={isComplete || i < cotProcessingSteps.length - 1 ? 'complete' : 'loading'}\n   186→\t\t\t\t\t\tanimate={!isInitialRender}\n   187→\t\t\t\t\t/>\n   188→\t\t\t\t\t<StatusItemText>\n   189→\t\t\t\t\t\t<TitleContent>\n   190→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{step?.toolName ? getIconForTool(step.toolName, true) : null}\n   191→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<Title>\n   192→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<StreamText\n   193→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcontent={step.title || ''}\n   194→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tanimations={['fadeIn']}\n   195→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsep=\"word\"\n   196→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsimulateStreaming={true}\n   197→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/>\n   198→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</Title>\n   199→\t\t\t\t\t\t</TitleContent>\n   200→\t\t\t\t\t\t{step.detail && (\n   201→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<Detail>\n   202→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<StreamText\n   203→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcontent={step.detail || ''}\n   204→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tanimations={['fadeIn']}\n   205→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsep=\"word\"\n   206→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsimulateStreaming={true}\n   207→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/>\n   208→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</Detail>\n   209→\t\t\t\t\t\t)}\n   210→\t\t\t\t\t\t{step.actions && (\n   211→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ActionButtonRow>\n   212→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{step.actions.map((action, i) => (\n   213→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<Button key={i} size=\"small\" onClick={() => onActionButtonClicked(action)}>\n   214→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{action}\n   215→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</Button>\n   216→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t))}\n   217→\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ActionButtonRow>\n   218→\t\t\t\t\t\t)}\n   219→\t\t\t\t\t</StatusItemText>\n   220→\t\t\t\t</StatusItem>\n   221→\t\t\t))}\n   222→\t\t</Container>\n   223→\t)\n   224→}\n   225→\n   226→const Container = styled.div`\n   227→\tpadding: 16px 24px 12px 16px;\n   228→\t/* Removed overflow-y: auto to prevent scrollbars */\n   229→\toverflow: visible;\n   230→\n   231→\tdisplay: flex;\n   232→\tflex-direction: column;\n   233→\tgap: 16px;\n   234→\n   235→\twidth: 100%;\n   236→\n   237→\tbox-sizing: border-box;\n   238→`\n   239→\n   240→const DetailedStatusItem = styled.div`\n   241→\tdisplay: flex;\n   242→\tflex-direction: column;\n   243→\tgap: 8px;\n   244→\twidth: 100%;\n   245→`\n   246→\n   247→const TitleBar = styled.div`\n   248→\tdisplay: flex;\n   249→\talign-items: center;\n   250→\n   251→\tgap: 8px;\n   252→\n   253→\tcursor: pointer;\n   254→\tuser-select: none;\n   255→`\n   256→\n   257→const TitleContent = styled.div`\n   258→\tdisplay: flex;\n   259→\tflex-direction: row;\n   260→\tgap: 4px;\n   261→\talign-items: center;\n   262→`\n   263→\n   264→const Title = styled.div`\n   265→\tfont-family: ${tokens.fontFamilyBase};\n   266→\tfont-size: ${tokens.fontSizeBase300};\n   267→\tfont-weight: ${tokens.fontWeightSemibold};\n   268→\tline-height: ${tokens.lineHeightBase300};\n   269→\tcolor: ${tokens.colorNeutralForeground1};\n   270→`\n   271→\n   272→const Detail = styled.div`\n   273→\tfont-family: ${tokens.fontFamilyBase};\n   274→\tfont-size: ${tokens.fontSizeBase300};\n   275→\tfont-weight: ${tokens.fontWeightRegular};\n   276→\tline-height: ${tokens.lineHeightBase300};\n   277→\tcolor: ${tokens.colorNeutralForeground3};\n   278→`\n   279→\n   280→const CollapsibleContent = styled(motion.div)`\n   281→\toverflow: hidden;\n   282→\tdisplay: flex;\n   283→\tflex-direction: column;\n   284→\tgap: 8px;\n   285→`\n   286→\n   287→const ThoughtContainer = styled(motion.div)`\n   288→\tdisplay: flex;\n   289→\tflex-direction: column;\n   290→\tgap: 6px;\n   291→\tpadding-right: 24px;\n   292→\toverflow: hidden;\n   293→`\n   294→\n   295→const ActionsContainer = styled.div`\n   296→\tdisplay: flex;\n   297→\tgap: 4px;\n   298→\tflex-wrap: wrap;\n   299→`\n   300→\n   301→const BadgeContainer = styled(motion.div)`\n   302→\toverflow: hidden;\n   303→`\n   304→\n   305→const StyledBadge = styled(Badge)`\n   306→\tbackground: ${tokens.colorNeutralBackground3};\n   307→\tfont-weight: 400;\n   308→\